                <h1 class="color-white" data-verticalnav-customtitle="Forza Horizon 6 Launches This Week With DLSS" id="subnautica-2,-battlefield-6-season-3,-directive-8020-&amp;-blades-of-fire-are-out-now-with-dlss">Subnautica 2, Battlefield 6 Season 3, Directive 8020 &amp; Blades of Fire Are Out Now With DLSS</h1>
                <div class="color-dark-grey">
                 By <a href="/geforce/author/andrew-burnes/" class="author-link" target="_blank">Andrew Burnes</a> on May 13, 2026 | <span class="article-comp-tags"> <span class="tagItem"><a href="/geforce/tags/">Featured Stories</a></span> <span class="tagItem"><a href="/geforce/tags/">Frame Generation</a></span> <span class="tagItem"><a href="/geforce/tags/">GeForce RTX 50 Series</a></span> <span class="tagItem"><a href="/geforce/tags/">GeForce RTX GPUs</a></span> <span class="tagItem"><a href="/geforce/tags/">Multi Frame Generation</a></span> <span class="tagItem"><a href="/geforce/tags/">NVIDIA App</a></span> <span class="tagItem"><a href="/geforce/tags/">NVIDIA DLSS</a></span> </span>
                </div>
               </div>
