                    <div class="text-left lap-text-left tab-text-left mob-text-left">
                     <div class="description ">
                      <p>For an optimum experience in <em>Forza Horizon 6</em>, with the high frame rates shown above, be sure to download and install our new <a href="/geforce/news/forza-horizon-6-geforce-game-ready-driver/">GeForce Game Ready Driver</a>.</p>
