                    <div class="text-left lap-text-left tab-text-left mob-text-left">
                     <div class="description ">
                      <p>Season 3 launched yesterday, bringing players a reimagining of a classic <em>Battlefield 4</em> map, now called Railway to Golmud, which is the biggest map in <em>Battlefield 6 </em>to date. Set within Tajikistan after the events of the campaign, this fan favorite has been optimized to match <em>Battlefield 6</em>’s visual fidelity and gameplay. Then later in the season, another legendary map arrives, with an updated reimagining of <em>Battlefield 3</em>’s Grand Bazaar, called Cairo Bazaar.</p>
