                     <div class="description ">
                      <p>Learn more about <em>Resident Evil Requiem</em> on PC in <a href="/geforce/news/resident-evil-requiem-path-tracing-dlss-4-multi-frame-gen-out-now/">our comprehensive launch article</a>.</p>
